cdata.name: Legendary Coin
cdata.desc: Legendary Coin is a PoW/PoS hybrid. The Coin has a raft of features such as transaction fee destruction, messaging, with hourly and daily superblocks. There is a two minute block time with the reward halving every 64800 blocks. The PoW phase is limited to 10 million and the PoS has an annualised rate of 50%.
